Company Profile
UPDATES (10)
ASK  QUESTION







“In a world-gone-wild with connected devices, we are striving to put back the "I" in Internet. We enable normal everyday people to have the convenience of their very own Cloud System to manage their digital lives, completely in the safety and privacy of their own home. Which also means no storage limits, no monthly fees, and greater security and autonomy. We automate all of the technical know-how in a device that sits in the home rather than "somewhere out on the Internet".



AJ ONeal
Co-Founder & CTO, Daplie




Key Facts

$80+ billion: personal cloud market size by 2020
450%: estimated increase in paid cloud storage customers from 2016 to 2017
Design and Utility Patents (Pending)
Currently accepting Pre-Orders

Our Ambition
As a company and as individuals we believe that every time we use technology we become digital creators. Currently, most of our digital content and even memories are sitting on company servers around the world eliminating true ownership of our personal data. Starting with the 540+ million cloud storage customers sacrificing privacy and ownership for convenience, Daplie is creating a home cloud infrastructure that will eventually be the secure and convenient hub for all of our digital devices.



