Why I Like Daplie



The personal server is the next home appliance.  Over the next three years, traditional retail departments that carry static computer hard drives will transition into carrying dynamic servers that allow consumers to back up not just their computers but mobile devices all to the same central location and act as a more affordable, far more private solution than public cloud providers like Dropbox, Google Drive, and iCloud.



Josh Isabell

                Investor in Daplie. Partner and Co-Founder, Bentonville Merchants International, Inc.
                














